B-textEditor/
├── src/
│   ├── data.c        (Global data initialization)
│   ├── file_io.c     (File opening/saving)
│   ├── input.c       (Key processing)
│   ├── main.c        (Entry point and loop)
│   ├── output.c      (Drawing to screen)
│   ├── row.c         (Row operations)
│   └── terminal.c    (Raw mode and low-level utils)
├── include/
│   ├── common.h      (Standard libraries and defines)
│   ├── data.h        (Structs and externs)
│   └── prototypes.h  (Function declarations)
├── Makefile          (Build script)
└── README.md
